<a href="/questions/128292-been-on-my-shelf-for-four-years---should-i">Been on my shelf for four years - should I read it??</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_128292'><a id="like_count_community_question_128292" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/128292?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">26 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6101138-wolf-hall">like</a></span>

