<a href="/questions/367262-i-found-this-book-difficult-to-read">I found this book difficult to read, because one had to constantly refer to family trees. If I left it for a few days I almost had to start again. Not sure it is one I would recommend as a MUST read....anyone think differently?</a>
</div>
