<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I agree. I feel that I am extremely well-versed in the topic and I can&apos;t imagine anyone who doesn&apos;t already know the details of the events being able <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I agree. I feel that I am extremely well-versed in the topic and I can't imagine anyone who doesn't already know the details of the events being able to read this. Plus, the writing style does not always make it obvious what person the story is being told in - or who is even speaking for pages. I applaud the work, but not a fun read.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
